content: Theo Robert Warburton Goldberg is a combination of four names, three of which are surnames. Theo is a first name of Greek origin, which means "gift of God." Robert is a first name of Germanic origin, which means "bright fame." Warburton is a surname of English origin, which means "a settlement by a weir or dam." Goldberg is a surname of Jewish (Ashkenazic) origin, which means "gold mountain." When combined, these names create a unique and distinctive full name that reflects different cultural and linguistic heritages.
